PrecisAuthorize the Ministers of the Environment, Indian Affairs and Northern Development and Transport to enter into a Mackenzie River Basin General Agreement with the Provinces of British Columbia, Alberta and Saskatchewan, and with the Yukon Territory and Northwest Territories and authorize the Commissioner of the Yukon Territory and the Commissioner of the Northwest Territories to enter into the said Agreement.
